line_1: When first I gaed to woo my Jenny,
line_2: Ye then was trottan wi' your Minnie:

line_1: When first I gaed to woo my Jenny,
line_2: Tho' ye was trickie, slee an' funnie,

line_1: When first I gaed to woo my Jenny,
line_2: But hamely, tawie, quiet an' cannie,

line_1: In Public calls me Cousin Jenny;
